p: The best model was then evaluated on whether; there were substantial interactions between cases of RSV and HMPV (alternatively stated as ϕ RSV ≠ ϕ HMPV ≠ 0), the existence of the influence of RSV on HMPV ( ϕ RSV = 0, ϕ HMPV ≠ 0), the existence of the influence of HMPV on RSV ( ϕ HMPV = 0, ϕ RSV ≠ 0) or there were no interactions at all ( ϕ RSV = ϕ HMPV = 0).
